
Resnik's, Lin's, and Jiang and Conrath's

Knowledge based methods
  * Edge Based Method
     - Path Length Approach
          o Shortest Path Length
          o Weighted Shortest Path Length
     - Depth Relative Scaling
     - Conceptual Similarity
     - Normalized Path Length
     - Leacock & Chodorow
     - Wu and Palmer
  * Information Content based Method
  * Feature based Method
  * Overlap
     - Lesk

Statistical/ Corpus-Based Similarity
    * Latent Semantic Analysis (LSA)
    * Generalized Latent Semantic Analysis (GLSA)
    * Explicit Semantic Analysis (ESA)
    * Pointwise Mutual Information - Information Retrieval (PMI - IR)
    * Normalized Google Distance (NGD)
    * Hyperspace Analogue to Language (HAL)

String-Based Similarity Measure
    * Character-Based Similarity Measure
        - Longest Common Substring (LCS)
        - Damerau-Levenshtein
        - Jaro
        - Jaro-Winkler
        - Needleman-Wunsch
        - Smith-Waterman
        - n-gram
        - syntactic n-gram
    * Term-Based Similarity Measure
        - Block Distance
        - Cosine Similarity
        - Soft Cosine Similarity
        - Sorensen-Dice index
        - Euclidean Distance
        - Jaccard Index
        - Simple Matching Coefficient (SMC)
